snippet.title: SCARiEST DEER ATTACK in 99 Nights in the Forest!! Adley Niko & Navey hilarious moment in Roblox game
snippet.description:
JOIN THE FAM - https://www.youtube.com/@GforGaming

HEY EVERYBODY!! 

Another one of our favorite moments from our latest 99 Nights in the Forest video on G for Gaming! Here we had a crazy moment where we were getting attacked by the Deer and the Deer cult! Navey was pretty spooked and Adley was making sure everybody stayed safe inside the circle next to our campfire! Niko being Niko went crazy and was fighting off all of them with nothing but his axe for chopping wood!

enjoy some A for Adley videos: https://www.youtube.com/c/AforAdleyLe...
have a blast with our A for Adley Shorts: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCMHpfyAqrjrhn-mRS2bUL0g
